data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a coveted neighborhood! This spacious raised ranch offers the perfect blend of comfort and style, boasting 5 bedrooms spread across two beautifully finished levels. Step into a haven of modern living with recent updates that include new flooring, fresh paint, and ADT Security System for your peace of mind. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a welcoming space for both relaxation and entertainment.The main level features a chic design, while the lower level provides additional versatile space to suit your needs- whether it's a cozy family room, a home office, or a playroom for the kids.
